condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Cebu City BRT System Manager | Description :Enter into a contract with a legal entity to serve as the Cebu CityBRT system manager by September 30, 2017 | Due Date :30-Sep-2017

Finance Agreement :Legal, Financial and Institutional Framework | Description :Establish overall legal, financial and institutionalframework acceptable to the Bank for the operation and maintenance of the BRT system in Cebu City by June 30, 2016 | Due Date:30-Jun-2016

Finance Agreement :Project Management, Technical Support, Procurement, Monitoring and Evaluation | Description :Enter into acontract with a Technical Support Consultant to support the NPMO and PIU in project management, technical support, procurement,monitoring and evaluation by March 31, 2015 | Due Date :31-Mar-2015

Finance Agreement: Bus Operator(s) for the Cebu City BRT | Description :Ensure that services of one or more legal entities arecontracted to serve as bus operator(s) for the Cebu City BRT by March 31, 2018 | Due Date :31-Mar-2018
Finance Agreement: Financial Management, Procurement and Implementation | Description: Standard financial management, procurementand implementation covenants as tailored to the project.

Finance Agreement: Implementation Arrangement | Description :Appoint a financial management specialist and a procurement specialistto the PIU, with functions, qualifications, and terms of reference as indicated in the Project Implementation Plan | Due Date:27-Mar-2015

Finance Agreement: Preparation of Annual Work and Financial Plan and Safeguards Implementation | Description: Project-specificcovenants relating to: (a) preparation of annual work and financial plan for approval by the Bank; (b) implementation of theproject in accordance with the Environmental Impact Assessment (EIA), Social Management Plan (SMP), Resettlement Action Plan (RAP);and (c) key outcome indicators

Finance Agreement: Withdrawal Conditions | Description: No withdrawal shall be made for payments made prior to the date of thisAgreement, except that withdrawals up to an aggregate amount not to exceed $23,200 from IBRD Loan and $5,000 equivalent from CTFLoan may be made for payments made prior to this date but not on or after December 31, 2013.
